plwin_init:

Synopsis: Change the default startup settings for plot windows.

Syntax: plwin_init ( XP, YP, XLENG, YLENG, XOFF, YOFF )

Description:

	Set the default initial (startup) behavior for plot
	windows. If you have a particular configuration you like to
	use, it is customary to put a call to plwin_init() in your
	.rlabrc startup file.

	XP: The number of X-pixels (default: 0).

	YP: The number of Y-pixels (default: 0).

	XLENG: The X (width) page length dimension (default: 400).

	YLENG: The Y (height) page length dimension (default: 300).

	XOFF: The X offset (screen coordinate) (default: 200);

	YOFF: The Y offset (screen coordinate) (default: 200);
